Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说什么就说吧 我又没有拦着你\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You can talk, I'm not stopping you.
