Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人在这里待了一整天了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I've been here on my own all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的错\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}That's not my fault.
