Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想和别人说话 就去用约会软件\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}If you want to talk to someone, go on...Tinder.
