Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我们能为它做些什么吗\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Can we do anything for it, do you think?
