Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望它没有脑震荡\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Hopefully, it's not a concussion.
